Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ruler. You know, it's just the wrong\Ninstrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge judgmentalism is just the wrong\Ninstrument to apply to human life. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because human life is coming out of an\Nincredible complexity. The evolution of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness and all of its karmic\Nexpressions throughout all of time is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what accounts for this piece of dust\Nhere at this moment. What can you say
