Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of time since the beginning of time.\NFor a piece of dust to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this air has to be here. The barometric\Npressure has to be here. This room has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to be here.\NSedona has to be here. Has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Arizona. Arizona has to be in the\Ncountry. All that has to be on the
