Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved throughout all of time to\Naccount for this particular moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be judgmental about it seems sort\Nof inappropriate, right? We don't know
