Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,knowingness.\NSo what does humility means? Spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,work. Humility is of profound\Nimportance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It means I of myself as an ego and\Ncompletely unable to comprehend reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no way of knowing the truth of\Nanything. Much less can I discern its
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,karma. Therefore, all judgment is up to\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgment is mine, sayth the Lord.\NWhy? Because you're not capable of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not capable of it. You would have to\Nknow the totality of all of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time up to the point\Nof this little piece of dust right here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain one piece of dust, much less\Nanything as complex
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as the tribal wars that have been going\Non in the Middle East for thousands of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,years and will probably continue to.\NWhy? Because it serves that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If life on Earth is purgatorial,\Ncertainly not heavenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If human life on this planet is an\Naspect of purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then that which seems horrible to us is\Nnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when you've had enough\Nsuffering that you say, "Hey, there must
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,be a better way."\NIt's only because you find out this all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,leads you into agony that you finally\Ngive it up. Right? How does the spirit
