Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,worshiping itself as the ego as\Nmegalomania?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, we can't even judge the\Npurpose of human life itself, much less
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that occurs in it.\NOh boy.
