Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about purgatory. You're in it.\NEverybody worries about purgatory. It
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me laugh. Yeah.\NAll right. So, it means then that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically we've earned the right to be\Nin a place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,where we have a choice\Nand we can determine our own destiny by
